{"tid":343464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【槍決色魔】姦殺也門3歲女童 電視直播槍斃過程","createTime":"2017-08-01T12:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T04:52:18.000Z","uid":66260,"like":87,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14c562dc8e5b396b05d4c4e356a085ab206a78cb","tid":343464,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:58:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170801/57025670\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170801%2F57025670&d=g6HUuDliaoTZmEauGmvtRDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4e4d472d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170801%2F57025670&h=aef85e46\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170801/57025670</a><br />\n<br />\n也門一名姦殺3歲女童的男子，在首都薩那被當眾槍斃。<br />\n<br />\n41歲的馬格拉比（Muhammad al-Maghrabi）承認在伊斯蘭教開齋節首天，在屋內姦殺馬塔里（Rana Yahya Al-Matari），上周四由囚車押送到解放廣場，雙手被戴手銬，伏在一塊布上，法官宣讀判刑後，充當劊子手的警員用突擊步槍，近距離連開五槍擊斃馬格拉比。<br />\n由於被殺的是女童，這宗案尤其矚目。槍決過程全國電視直播，現場亦有幾千人圍觀，有人爬上電線杆或從樓宇天台觀看槍決過程，有人用手機拍攝。<br />\n當局慎防女童所屬部族有人向馬格拉比報復，囚車由五部警車護送。<br />\n根據伊斯蘭教法，謀殺可判死刑。<br />\n馬格拉比伏法之後，馬塔里的父親感到「獲得重生」，並得到安慰。<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"1378cfd64efd7af6f873f64e2e1788cdcc74d87e","tid":343464,"uid":117602,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb617e5551da9e5e20ea705541e1ffb8ddeb2441","tid":343464,"uid":66260,"like":82,"dislike":32,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:59:58.000Z","msg":"連登仔: 一定係3歲女童既錯, 累死41歲大好中年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a88028b64831176973f1aef40925942c1ce7a1","tid":343464,"uid":36451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl